Description: fetch YouTube transcripts and subtitles (Avalan PPA pin)
 youtube-transcript-api is a Python library that retrieves
 transcripts and subtitles from YouTube videos -- both manually
 supplied and auto-generated -- without driving a headless browser.
 Not in Debian; hand-packaged at 1.2.4 to satisfy Avalan's
 >= 1.2.2, < 2.0 constraint.
